  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK632">
<l>vaṉkaṇ kuṭikāttalkaṟ ṟaṟita lāḷviṉaiyō </l>
<l>ṭaintuṭaṉ māṇṭa tamaiccu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The minister is one who in addition to the aforesaid five things excels in the possession of firmness, protection of subjects, clearness by learning, and perseverance.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
